General introduction:
--------------------
	This is BibleTime @VERSION@ for KDE 3.
If you find bugs please report them to info@bibletime.info or use our
online bugreport form on www.bibletime.info.

Please do also send suggestions, criticism and moral support to info@bibletime.info.

Read the file INSTALL how to install and compile this version of BibleTime.
The AUTHORS file contains a list of authors working on BibleTime.
There's also a SPEC file to create RPMs, it's called bibletime.spec.

This README file contains some very useful instructions and tips how to use BibleTime.
Please read also the new handbook, it contains many instructions about the usage and
installation of BibleTime.


Requirements
------------
	o QT 3.0.x or later
	o KDE 3.x
	o SWORD 1.5.5

Documentation:
--------------
We do have a really useful handbook now!
Fred did a great job with it and worked long on it. We hope that you like it.
You can read the handbook in the help browser of KDE. It's in the Applications section.

